        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <Section id="problem" title="The Hidden Cause of Stubborn Fat" subtitle="Harvard scientists discovered a shocking truth...">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border-l-4 border-primary-500">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <strong>Low mitochondria levels</strong> is the one common factor in every overweight person. Your mitochondria are tiny "energy engines" in your cells that burn fat and create ATP energy.
